cz.muni.fi.virtualtoolmanager.pubapi.entities

Class SearchCriteria.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.muni.fi.virtualtoolmanager.pubapi.entities.SearchCriteria.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    SearchCriteria

    public static class SearchCriteria.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents a key part of so called Builder pattern. Static class Builder is used only for more transparent, easier and faster set up of SearchCriteria attributes.
